{"tid":2421990,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"ZARA新品激似日本學校運動衫 網民笑言：世界終於追上日本時裝品味","createTime":"2021-02-25T01:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T08:31:29.000Z","uid":41343,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a164ae4f9ed16645f847dbd02f40203513fb453d","tid":2421990,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"時裝潮流日新月異，近年正吹起一鼓運動休閒風，甚至已經成為主流趨勢，就算日常逛街配搭運動裝束亦見怪不怪。最近ZARA推出春裝單品，讓日本網民馬上聯想到學校的體育服設計而引起熱議，有網民更笑言「世界終於追趕上日本的時裝品味」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這套引起熱烈討論的ZARA新品，以滾邊設計、分別推出羅紋上衣及短版T恤兩款，配以同系列滾邊短褲，與日本的學校運動服（體操服）相似度十足，而且ZARA推出紅色、深藍色及黑色三款顏色，均與學校體操服不謀而合。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TMErhrm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMErhrm.jpg&h=c8bd30e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GuMtvMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGuMtvMn.jpg&h=27cd1217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUXTGTb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUXTGTb.jpg&h=e19334e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAuF6jS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAuF6jS.jpg&h=848198db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f3ef1746c51f5c8aff20dcdaed67913aa1a829a","tid":2421990,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T01:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f3729acb5084735a0e9064643a541827022fa1","tid":242